author: gartung
body:
#### PR description:
Change the end point function regex to deprecated_get to restore missing call stacks. NetworkX did not form a path from a top level function to the end point function unless get was changed to the newly defined deprecated_get.

#### PR validation:
Ran locally to verify that missing calls stacks were added back to report.
title: Utilities/StaticAnalyzer: Update ESR::get report generator with deprecated_get end point function.
